 Documentation Categories:

1. Architecture (arch/*)
   - System design documents
   - Component interactions
   - Data flow diagrams

2. API Reference (api/*)
   - Public API documentation
   - Tool interfaces
   - Configuration schemas

3. User Guides (guides/*)
   - Installation instructions
   - Usage examples
   - Configuration guides
   - Best practices

4. Development (dev/*)
   - Contributing guidelines
   - Development setup
   - Testing procedures
   - Release process

5. Tool Documentation (tools/*)
   - Individual tool documentation
   - Language-specific guides
   - Integration guides

Cross-referencing:
- Use @file to reference specific files
- Use #section for doc sections
- Use [link text](mdc:path) for links
- Keep paths relative to docs root